"title": "5878: honour",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5878",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Great respect; the creation is called upon to respect and revere God as its Creator. Since human beings are made in the image of God, they should respect one another.</p>\n<h2>The creation honours its Creator</h2>\n<h3>All creatures honour God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:20\">ISA 43:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13\">REV 5:13</a></p>\n<h3>The people of God honour God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:40-Exod12:42\">EXO 12:40–12:42</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:23\">PSA 22:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:14-Ps50:15\">PSA 50:14–50:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:1-Isa25:3\">ISA 25:1–25:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:17\">JER 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:7-Jer33:9\">JER 33:7–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:1\">2TH 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>How God wishes to be honoured</h2>\n<h3>Honouring God by worshipping him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:11-Rev5:12\">REV 5:11–5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:23\">PSA 50:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:9-Rev4:11\">REV 4:9–4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Honouring God by obeying him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:31\">EZK 33:31</a></strong> <em>These people honoured God with their words only, but this was not true honour for they failed to obey his commands.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:10-Num25:13\">NUM 25:10–25:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></p>\n<h3>Honouring God with one's body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10-2Cor4:11\">2CO 4:10–4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Honouring God with one's possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9\">PRO 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:9\">ISA 60:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:19\">2CO 8:19</a></p>\n<h3>Honouring God by caring for others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:31–25:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of not honouring God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:2\">MAL 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:12\">NUM 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22-Dan5:31\">DAN 5:22–5:31</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ and honour</h2>\n<h3>Honour given to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:17\">ACT 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17\">2PE 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a></p>\n<h3>The relationship of honour between the Father and the Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:23\">JHN 5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:49-John8:50\">JHN 8:49–8:50</a></p>\n<h2>God brings honour to people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:30\">1SA 2:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:7\">PSA 62:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:19-Zeph3:20\">ZEP 3:19–3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:9-Rom2:11\">ROM 2:9–2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Honouring others as a duty to God</h2>\n<h3>Honouring one's parents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:2-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:2–6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:6\">MAT 15:1–15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a></p>\n<h3>Honouring fellow believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:10\">ROM 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:29\">PHP 2:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17\">1TI 5:17</a></p>",
